Name: Greater Lokir Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Lokir Rune, Level 3 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes trickery and cunning, allowing those who channel it the ability to manipulate the conniving darkness.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACEBackstabSPACEAs a bonus action, you conjure a dagger into your hand for TIME2-4TIME rounds and can make a melee spell attack with the dagger against a creature within reach as an action on each of your turns. On a hit, the target takes psychic damage equal to DAMAGE2-4DAMAGEd10 + your Charisma modifier and must make a Wisdom saving throw. On a failed save, you become invisible to the target until the start of your next turn.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 4 runic attunement slots. Requires Charisma 16 or greater to attune.
